description:
&lt;p&gt;An amazing opportunity has arisen for a Vascular Specialist Nurse to join a team of dedicated clinicians delivering Vascular services to patients across Morecambe Bay area. This is a perfect development opportunity for a senior nurse with experience in Vascular Surgery to work alongside a fantastic and welcoming team. Could this be you?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be a key member of the Vascular Surgery Team and as an autonomous practitioner; they will be responsible for developing and leading a comprehensive service for managing vascular patients. The post holder must be dynamic and proactive. A team player is essential with the ability to communicate effectively within the service and with patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant for this job role would be supported to develop their clinical and leadership skills. A tailor made programme of development would be undertaken dependent on skill set and experience. The successful applicant will need to be able to travel across site within the Morecambe Bay Zone to support this growing service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview Date: To be confirmed&lt;/p&gt;
